Package: maker
Type: Package
Title: Makefile generator for R analytical projects
Version: 0.1
Author: Michal Burda
Maintainer: Michal Burda <michal.burda@osu.cz>
Description: Tool for creating and maintaining a build process of complex analytic tasks in R.
  It allows to easily generate Makefile for the 'make' tool, which drives the build process
  by (paralelly) executing build commands accordingly to given dependencies between source files
  and generated data files and/or reports.
License: GPL (>= 3.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: tools, pryr, assertthat, rmarkdown
Suggests: testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
